Recipes</h2>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5872\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fiRrmks.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"286\" />\nIron Generator\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5873\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zrTdRWl.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"252\" height=\"128\" />\n\nGold Generator\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5874\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JS45C7c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"252\" height=\"129\" />\n\nDiamond Generator\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5875\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IdLLbbV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"128\" />\n\nObsidian Generator\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2>Modpacks</h2>\nDon't ask just add. A link back here would be nice but not required.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2>Streams/Tubers</h2>\nYes, please. Share the stream and video link in the comments below and I'll add it to the overview. That's free advertising for you!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5876 size-large\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/bh_bg_config-1024x100.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"100\" />\n<h2>How To Configure It</h2>\n<p><a href/embed/QqHvKVcgWdI?wmode=transparent\">Video Demonstration</a></p>\n\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>This project is proudly powered by FORGE</strong>, without whom it would not be possible. Help FORGE get rid of Adfocus at <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/LexManos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.patreon.com/LexManos</a>.\n\n&nbsp;",
